  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0"><a href="/hashtag/RemembranceSunday?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>RemembranceSunday</b></a> 
Remembering all those who gave their lives for our freedom today. Thank you</p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0"><a href="/hashtag/20mph?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>20mph</b></a>=Safer streets + more <a href="/hashtag/walking?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>walking</b></a> &amp; <a href="/hashtag/cycling?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>cycling</b></a>. Good news for our children. I have joined <a href="/livingstreets" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="18045594"><s>@</s><b>livingstreets</b></a>. <a href="/hashtag/Love20mph?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Love20mph</b></a> <a href="http://t.co/jxaH1HJvQh" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://bit.ly/love20T" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://bit.ly/love20T"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">bit.ly/love20T</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
